{"tid":1876152,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"【油魔當道】本港燃油零售價四年升4成　車主捱貴油多付3元一升","createTime":"2020-02-12T08:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T09:24:29.000Z","uid":57182,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e91ab3b3b52ac214dd178e5828487e59271c78","tid":1876152,"uid":57182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:27:24.000Z","msg":"進口價及國際油價　四年僅升1成<br />\n<br />\n根據消委會數據比較過去五年數據，發現油公司的價格在2015年10月至2019年間持續上升，每公升車用燃油零售價(扣除每升6.06元稅項)，由2015年10月的7.78元，升至今年2月的10.63元，四年間累升接近4成。而同期車用燃油進口價僅升11%，國際原油價格亦只升12%，車用油價升幅大幅跑贏國際油價約30個百分點。以一位私家車車主入40公升油計，四年間每升多付3元，變相多付約120元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200212/INZILV2TDD3DJVAIQDZDPDQQ5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200212%2FINZILV2TDD3DJVAIQDZDPDQQ5Y%2F&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GP2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=12a7cb71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200212%2FINZILV2TDD3DJVAIQDZDPDQQ5Y%2F&h=c2516f1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200212/INZILV2TDD3DJVAIQDZDPDQQ5Y/</a>"},{"pid":"20c0a99a3dc481bf5b22b1be7289c11f1241601f","tid":1876152,"uid":57182,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:29:58.000Z","msg":"競爭法係咪已經失效？<br />\n香港政府再唔控制好個油價，一定愈黎愈多車主考慮電動車，起碼電個價穩定好多<br />\n<br />\n不過講真，等得政府幫忙，香港人可能自己研發到自主汽油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b574d4e3f4241098748526ea34b068f09db3d0cd","tid":1876152,"uid":156542,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:32:28.000Z","msg":"香港得98油 <br />\n根本入95就夠 焗你入貴油 無咁嘅需要<br />\n啲油公司夾好曬 一齊加價 一齊用98油"},{"pid":"af73e9347e5ed47f22b02c61f8c8f055b506e9f3","tid":1876152,"uid":10274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:36:44.000Z","msg":"油公司仆街....真係唔係第一日知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed664a551dd1f191f827c443c3ad072f80e7